name: Psychofactory
description:
A psychopath worker is trying to demolish every product to avoid it from going to it's respective owner. 

Make the shipping process fail to progress.

Credits:

Saidus - Programming / Game Design

Madsdev - Art / Game Design

Tallbeard Studios /  Nicole Marie T - Sound Design

DISCLAIMER: You might encounter an error called "TypeError: Cannot set property 'onclick' of null" before playing the game. Just click "Ok" to continue the game!
